data.description: This stunning and spacious single story home is comprised of five total bedrooms and four total bathrooms over 2,798 square feet on a sprawling 20,473 square foot lot, offering a perfect combination of modern living and convenient location. Boasting luxurious features and conveniences, along with an open concept floor plan and an awe-inspiring resort inspired backyard, this property is an ideal haven for anyone seeking an extraordinary place to call home.  The spacious living area is an inviting space complete with a cozy fireplace set against a custom marble accent wall.  The modern chef's kitchen is equipped with state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances. Whole-home automation provides for convenient control of lighting, climate, security, and audio throughout the home. A resort-inspired pool and spa, complete with beach deck entry, water features and fire pit, as well as a swim-up sunken covered bar and outdoor kitchen area provides for a tranquil and inviting space to entertain.
